On this episode of ANN International, learn how local pastors in Mexico plan to refocus ministry efforts to increase effective evangelism. 

The good news of salvation touches the hearts of eight hundred people in India. 

An ADRA Romania & Moldova conference gathers resources to support Türkiye. 

Plus, the Peruvian Ministry of Health responds to Seventh-day Adventist worker's request not to work on Sabbaths.

Stay tuned as ANN brings you these captivating stories and provides coverage of other global news. For a deeper dive into these headlines, visit adventist.news.
